{"comments":"Text Operations — Manipulation and query functions for shaped text\n\nProvides utilities for:\n- Truncation: Cutting text to fit within bounds\n- Filtering: Culling off-screen glyphs\n- Comparison: Testing glyph equality and ordering\n- Sorting: Arranging glyphs by position\n\n## Dependencies\n- Hydrogen.GPU.Text.Types\n- Hydrogen.GPU.Text.Internal\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Truncate shaped text to fit within maxWidth\n\nRemoves glyphs that extend beyond maxWidth. If truncation occurs,\nthe text is cut at the last glyph that fully fits. For ellipsis\ntruncation, the caller should append \"...\" to the truncated text.\n\nUses comparison operators (>, >=, <) for bounds checking.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Text","Types"],"ShapedText"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Text","Types"],"ShapedText"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,51],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Text/Operations.purs","start":[71,1]},"title":"truncateText"},{"children":[],"comments":"Filter glyphs to only those currently visible\n\nRemoves glyphs that are completely outside the visible region.\nUseful for culling off-screen text in scrolling views.\n\nUses Data.Array.filter for efficient predicate-based selection.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents